6.2.2.7 Complex keys
....................

The query `startkey=["foo"]&endkey=["foo",{}]' will match most array
keys with "foo" in the first element, such as `["foo","bar"]' and
`["foo",["bar","baz"]]'. However it will not match
`["foo",{"an":"object"}]'


