7.3.2 Logging API
-----------------

There's also an API for adding messages to CouchDB's logs. Its simply:

    ["log", $MESG]\n

Where `$MESG' is any arbitrary JSON. There is no response from this
command. As with the config API, the trailing `\n' represents a newline
byte.


