revision and ID information:

    HTTP/1.1 201 Created
    Cache-Control: must-revalidate
    Content-Length: 215
    Content-Type: application/json
    Date: Sat, 26 Oct 2013 00:10:39 GMT
    Server: CouchDB (Erlang OTP)

